Invocation Name: church of lakes
des:
Listen to the latest sermons from Presbyterian Church of the Lakes in Orlando, FL. You can pause and play by saying "Alexa, pause" and "Alexa, resume." Just say "Alexa, stop" when you're done for the day. When listening you can say "Alexa, shuffle" to shuffle the playing order, or "Alexa, loop" to loop the current episode. You can also ask for previous and next sermons by saying "Alexa, previous" and "Alexa, next". The most recent sermon will always be played first.

Visit us at https://www.pcol.org.
